    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/130922234/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">袁小圆</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-05-20"
      class="main-meta">2016-05-20 08:52:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7902654_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   在浩瀚的文学长河中，《黑麋鹿如是说》应该是唯一一本广为传颂的描写北美印第安人的著作。看此书之前，我对印第安人知之甚少，只听说过。他们在我脑海中是那种头插羽毛的，喜欢在脸上涂着油彩，经常围着篝火跳舞的少数民族。他们文明不发达，才会是仿佛生活在过去的原始人，靠...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7902654/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7902654_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7902654_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










